  <div metal:fill-slot="content">

  <div id="content">
    <h1>Community</h1> 
    <p>The BFG community makes heavy use of IRC chats for staying in touch and helping out new developers. Please join us at the <a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/#repoze">#repoze channel</a> for support, rants, raves or just plain lurking.</p>
    <p>We also have some tools available for you:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Need to discuss some piece of code at the IRC channel? Use our <a href="${application_url}/pastebin">Pastebin</a>.</li>
      <li>Have a piece of code you are proud of or something you think worth learning but don't have time to write a long blog post or tutorial? Why not just paste it and add a brief explanation on our <a href="${application_url}/tutorialbin">quick and dirty tutorial maker</a>.</li>
      <li>If you prefer to use mailing lists for support and collaboration, you can use the <a href="http://lists.repoze.org/listinfo/repoze-dev">repoze.dev mailing list</a>, but be warned that it is a very low volume list, since we are usually on IRC.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  </div>
